# Combining Precision Tuning and Rewriting

This file is a transition-time build anchor for the public page.
The canonical publication record and assets live in
`pubs/2021-arith-herbie/`.

Edit `pubs/2021-arith-herbie/publication.json` for structured publication
data, keep the abstract/BibTeX/assets in the same directory, and use
`pubs/2021-arith-herbie/extra.dj` for any rare page-specific extra content.
